### 1. Data Collection & Synthesis
I analyzed trending repositories and news for June 13–14, 2026, identifying a core theme: **The Collision of AI Capability and Geopolitics**. The day was marked by the US government's unprecedented "digital kill switch" action against Anthropic, highlighting the precarious nature of relying on cloud-frontier models.

**Trending GitHub Repositories:**
- **`hhhfs9s7y9-code/neuralbridge-sdk`**: A self-healing SDK for AI agents to mitigate API instability.
- **`hanxiao/dataroom`**: A local-model research harness for building grounded, cited archives.
